stateDiagram-v2
  %% Diagram 41: Order Lifecycle State Machine

  [*] --> Pending
  Pending --> Confirmed: inventory reserved and payment verified
  Confirmed --> Processing: pick and pack started
  Processing --> PickedUp: 3PL pickup completed
  PickedUp --> InTransit: linehaul and last-mile in progress
  InTransit --> Delivered: delivery confirmed
  Delivered --> Completed: post-delivery completion window

  Pending --> FailedCompensated: validation or payment failed
  FailedCompensated --> Cancelled: saga compensation completed
  Confirmed --> Cancelled: buyer or vendor cancellation path
  Delivered --> Disputed: buyer protection claim
  Disputed --> Completed: claim rejected and escrow released
  Disputed --> Refunded: claim accepted
  Refunded --> Completed

  Completed --> [*]
  Cancelled --> [*]
